### Maintenance

- Bump @actions/core from 1.2.7 to 1.9.1 (#131) [@mjayaram](https://github.com/mjayaram)
- Upgrade action runtime from node12 to node16 (#141) [@mjayaram](https://github.com/mjayaram)

